Last week I had the pleasure of staying at @legermainhotels in Toronto and had the most incredible experience from beginning to end! ✨

Some of my favourite things were their extremely spacious rooms and bathrooms, spa-like high pressure showers, rooftop golfing and terrace, as well as their in-hotel restaurant @victorrestaurant that had impeccable service and mouth watering dishes. 

There were also so many little details at @legermainhotels that elevated my stay, such as the complimentary earplugs placed on the nightstand, the extra large shower towels that comfortably wrapped around my body, and the fully stocked coffee/tea bar and mini fridge. 

If you want to have a luxurious stay during your next visit to Toronto, make sure you check into @legermainhotels! 🤍

@deltavancouver ☁️✨

My first visit to Vancouver would not have been complete without my stay at the @deltavancouver. 

I had an incredible experience at this hotel as their suits feature a separate bedroom and living area and is 35% larger than the average hotel room. My room even included a personal balcony where I could enjoy city views and my morning coffee. 

Their hotel restaurant @stockandsupplyvan had great dishes including the “Turkish Eggs” which I highly recommend.

If you’re looking for a hotel in the heart of Vancouver, @deltavancouver is the place for you.
